{
  "page": "War Across the Water",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0C4DE;\">War Across the Water<br />Worthless War</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Battles</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> rule over the Three Sisters established and consolidated</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"text-align:left; background:none\">\n  <tbody><tr><td width=\"50%\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Belligerents</td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/45px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/60px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_North\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingdom of the North\">Kingdom of the North</a></b>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>\n<dl><dd><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Bolton.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/25px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"28\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/38px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/50px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a></dd></dl></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/45px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/60px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingdom of Mountain and Vale\">Kingdom of Mountain and Vale</a></b>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>\n<dd><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Sunderland.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Sunderland.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/25px-House_Sunderland.svg.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"28\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/38px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/50px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Sunderland\" title=\"House Sunderland\">House Sunderland</a>\n<dl><dd><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Borrell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Borrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/25px-House_Borrell.svg.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"28\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/38px-House_Borrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Borrell.svg/50px-House_Borrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Borrell\" title=\"House Borrell\">House Borrell</a></dd>\n<dd><a href=\"/index.php/House_Longthorpe\" title=\"House Longthorpe\">House Longthorpe</a></dd>\n<dd><a href=\"/index.php/House_Torrent\" title=\"House Torrent\">House Torrent</a></dd></dl></dd></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Bolton.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Bolton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/20px-House_Bolton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/30px-House_Bolton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0c/House_Bolton.svg/40px-House_Bolton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Belthasar_Bolton\" title=\"Belthasar Bolton\">Belthasar Bolton</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/20px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/40px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Mathos_II_Arryn\" title=\"Mathos II Arryn\">Mathos II Arryn</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/20px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/40px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Osgood_Arryn\" title=\"Osgood Arryn\">Osgood Arryn</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Arryn.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Arryn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/20px-House_Arryn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/30px-House_Arryn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Arryn.svg/40px-House_Arryn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Oswin_Arryn\" title=\"Oswin Arryn\">Oswin Arryn</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>War Across the Water</b>, known to some as the <b>Worthless War</b>, was a war between the <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of Mountain and Vale\">Kings of Mountain and Vale</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_in_the_North\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings in the North\">Kings in the North</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> over control of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_Across_the_Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The war was the result of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a> two thousand years ago, when <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> occupied the previously-independent islands known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>. In response, the <a href=\"/index.php/Pirate\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pirate\">pirate</a> kings of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a> bent the knee to King <a href=\"/index.php/Mathos_II_Arryn\" title=\"Mathos II Arryn\">Mathos II Arryn</a> in exchange for the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>'s assistance in driving out the northmen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Mathos sailed for <a href=\"/index.php/Sisterton\" title=\"Sisterton\">Sisterton</a> with a hundred warships. Although he never returned from war, his sons and descendants continued the fight against the northmen for a thousand years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Control of the Three Sisters changed more than twelve times. Northmen landed on the <a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a> three times;<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> King <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Stark\" title=\"Theon Stark\">Theon Stark</a> once conquered the islands and landed an army on the Fingers,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> though it is unknown if this was part of the Worthless War or during a different time. A northern castle, the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf%27s_Den\" title=\"Wolf&#39;s Den\">Wolf's Den</a> at the mouth of the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Knife\" title=\"White Knife\">White Knife</a>, was besieged by King <a href=\"/index.php/Osgood_Arryn\" title=\"Osgood Arryn\">Osgood Arryn</a> and burned by his son, <a href=\"/index.php/Oswin_Arryn\" title=\"Oswin Arryn\">Oswin the Talon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Starks</a> attacked <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> in response and, unable to overcome its walls, burned hundreds of ships in the city's harbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The war eventually ended when House Stark simply lost interest in controlling the Three Sisters.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_Across_the_Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The war is described in Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Perestan\" title=\"Perestan\">Perestan</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Consideration_of_History\" title=\"A Consideration of History\">A Consideration of History</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Rule by the triumphant <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">Arryns</a> over the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> has remained tenuous.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Some <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a> still resent <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> for the invasion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_Across_the_Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>When his lady wife questioned the wisdom of involving the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale</a> in this War Across the Water, <a href=\"/index.php/Mathos_II_Arryn\" title=\"Mathos II Arryn\">His Grace</a> famously replied that he would sooner have <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">a pirate</a> than <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">a wolf</a> for his neighbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>This was not a case of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> winning so much as <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> losing interest. For ten long centuries <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">the direwolf</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">the falcon</a> had fought and bled over <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">three rocks</a>, until one day the wolf awoke as from a dream and realized it was only stone between his teeth, whence he spat it out and walked away.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Perestan\" title=\"Perestan\">Perestan</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/A_Consideration_of_History\" title=\"A Consideration of History\">A Consideration of History</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">The wolf</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">the falcon</a> fought over us for a thousand years, till between the two of them they had gnawed all the fat and flesh off the bones of <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">these poor islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Godric_Borrell\" title=\"Godric Borrell\">Godric Borrell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_Across_the_Water&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.7</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D